{"word":"ὁτιή","slug":"ὁτιή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁτιή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Comic form of <el>ὅτι</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>because</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <el>ὅτι</el>, <i>that</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <el>ὅ τι</el>, <i>wherefore</i>, <el>ὁτιὴ τί</el>; <i>why so? wherefore so?</i> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}